{"word":"Kirjathaim","slug":"kirjathaim","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Kirjathaim</b> <a href=\"#/H7156\">H7156</a> <br/> 1. Called Kiriathaim:<br/> - A city of Reuben<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=32&verse=37'>Num 32:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=13&verse=19'>Jos 13:19</a> <br/> - Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=48&verse=1'>Jer 48:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=48&verse=23'>Jer 48:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=25&verse=9'>Eze 25:9</a> <br/> 2. A Levitical city in Naphtali<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=76'>1Ch 6:76</a>"}]}